<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />俗话说<delay8 />
一年之计在于春。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在正认真考虑<delay20 />
今年要不要<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />培养一些<delay8 />新的兴趣呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">一旦习惯了炎热的天气，<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉还挺不错的呢。<10_4 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喝冰镇的冰茶时，<delay20 />
会觉得格外美味哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起秋天就会联想到读书之秋呢。<10_4 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想趁着这个机会<delay20 />试着读一些<delay8 />
以前<delay8 />不怎么会接触的书。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">一到冬天，<delay8 /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就会特别想吃<delay20 />
热乎乎的料理呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也正在<delay8 />研究一些<delay8 />新式火锅，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等完成之后，<delay8 />
我会请大家来吃的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如今正值春色满园的时节！<delay frames="40" />
这微暖的春风，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真叫人心情舒畅。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />夏天<delay8 />会让人变得特别直率呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我要不要也下定决心<delay20 />
发表一下自己创作的诗歌呀。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">总觉得秋天<delay8 />弥漫着一股浪漫气息呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虫鸣细碎<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />秋色染上枝头<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />好像能写出一首好诗。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一到冬天，脚部就会觉得特别冷呢～<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过只要勤加活动，一下就暖和起来了。<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我得多散散步才行！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="10" arg="0x66 0x65 0x65 0x65 0x66 0x66" /></message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="10" arg="0x68 0x67 0x67 0x67 0x68 0x68" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="10" arg="0x6a 0x69 0x69 0x69 0x6a 0x6a" /></message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="10" arg="0x6c 0x6b 0x6b 0x6b 0x6c 0x6c" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />天气渐暖，<delay8 />虫子都开始频繁活动起来了呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也是被这勃勃生机吸引，<delay20 />
才决定到外面来走走的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得<delay8 />春天有种独特的气息呢。<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是这种<delay8 />轻飘飘软绵绵的感觉<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道你能不能理解我的意思。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
这个时期天气特别炎热，<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />请你一定要注意补充水分哦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />夏天<delay20 />有种独特的氛围呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比起正午时分，<delay20 />这个时间段
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />更能体会到那种感觉哦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />秋色渐浓，<delay20 />
就连这个时间段，也非常舒适呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像正适合悠闲地看看书。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我感觉到了秋天的气息！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一到这个季节<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />人总是会变得多愁善感起来呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">冬天虽然非常寒冷，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过比起晚上，<delay8 />白天还是要暖和多了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Shaking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像也暖和不了多少呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这凛冽<delay20 />的寒气<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />冬天的氛围真是太棒了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
